HEADWORD: Knapweed
<hw>Knap"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The black centaury (<spn>Centaurea nigra</spn>); -- so called from
the knoblike heads of flowers. Called also
<altname>bullweed</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
